10. Range

range(5)        # 0-4
range(1, 5)     # 1-4
range(1, 10, 2) # step


⸻

11. Enumerate & Zip

Enumerate

lst = ["a", "b", "c"]

for i, val in enumerate(lst):
    print(i, val)


⸻

Zip

a = [1, 2]
b = ["x", "y"]

for x, y in zip(a, b):
    print(x, y)


⸻

12. List Comprehension

nums = [1, 2, 3, 4]

squares = [x**2 for x in nums]
print(squares)


⸻

With Condition

evens = [x for x in nums if x % 2 == 0]


⸻

13. Lambda Functions

Syntax

lambda arguments: expression


⸻

Example

add = lambda a, b: a + b
print(add(2, 3))


⸻

With map()

nums = [1, 2, 3]

result = list(map(lambda x: x * 2, nums))


